  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> flaked almonds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden, then set aside and reserve the pan</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
