      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the green stalk off the <strong>aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>and discard, then chop into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped aubergine</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until slightly softened and charred</p>",
      "order": 3,
