    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the aubergine is cooking, boil half a kettle</p><p>Slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>halloumi </strong>into small bite-size cubes</p>",
