    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine is slightly softened, reduce the heat to medium-high and add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and <strong>garlic </strong>with a little drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the onion has begun to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>parsely</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
